# Copy to dashboard/.env (or .env.local) — never commit the copy.
#
# Target for the /v1/* + /v1/stream Vite dev-server proxy (vite.config.ts).
# NOT VITE_-prefixed on purpose: this is read at vite.config.ts's own
# Node-side config-eval time, not by client code via import.meta.env.
#
# - Real bifrostd (docker compose up, see deploy/README.md): 127.0.0.1:8391
#   (published by deploy/docker-compose.dev.yml's netbase service).
# - Mock bifrostd (`npm run mock` in this directory, no Docker stack needed):
#   also 127.0.0.1:8391 by default (MOCK_PORT env var to change it).
BIFROSTD_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8391
